			<div class="content" id="post-content-2429083">
									

<p>Code Brown, which as we all know, stands for a Bright family reunion.</p>
<p>I feel like this is currently the longest story I have written for this site. It was supposed to be a short and cute little thing, but then I needed all the right characters and&#8230; *shrugs*</p>
<p>this story goes out to my fans, the people who take the time to see all the little twists and turns of the whole intricate plot line. See? It all starts to make sense, ey?</p>

